DTEND:20261017T210000
DESCRIPTION:This course will give students a foundational education in timb
 er framing while they work as a group to build and complete a timber frame
  pavilion. Students will gain an understanding of the materials\, tools an
 d safety standards used in the timber framing industry.
SUMMARY:Timber Framing
